{"tid":472110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱聽到有阿伯講:「李飛呢啲「二打六」官員」","createTime":"2017-11-18T01:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T02:53:14.000Z","uid":142888,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c697180669d0433d35e7d9ac9db6b85d0d6538c0","tid":472110,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">啱啱肚痛去商場廁所，聽到2個阿伯，響到吹水，有一個帶著眼鏡兼有啲似鄭少秋嘅阿伯(髮型一樣，不過矮過鄭少秋)屌樓下嗰日本拉麵店賣70蚊一碗麵，屌屌下唔知點解開始屌李飛。</span><br />\n<br />\n阿伯：乜嘢李飛乜嘢基本法委員，都唔撚知佢邊個黎，唔撚識佢啊。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，佢講幾句嘢，啲特區高官就完全附和，又話要搞返23條，之前03年有50萬人上街都仲敢搞，擺明違反民意，都唔知做乜撚嘢，冇事搵事黎搞。<br />\n<br />\n我之前都唔識李飛，佢真係「唔臭米氣」<br />\n<br />\n唔通響嗰啲香港特區高官眼中 李飛呢啲「二打六」外來官員嘅重要性仲大過 全港市民!?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我好鐘意聽阿伯講新聞，除咗中point之外，把老牛聲都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6a2994e82b2163c0838fcbf401ec42c99321fc31","tid":472110,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"你見點?個肚好返d未"},{"pid":"8070adea9f52365ba304321a56ffde1214afaf48","tid":472110,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你見點?個肚好返d未</blockquote><br />\n其實係聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我聽聲就認得，因為佢係我做緊part time 嗰到嘅清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eed913c671a4ecb59c8e24684ae2930dc74c82","tid":472110,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7becd199ea3ce60a2915a9644fc505bd4f13df","tid":472110,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"基本法大廈看更"}]}